-CASE SerialManyDuplicateIntIDsIgnoreErrors
# If the vector size is 2 the CSV can be read with multiple threads which makes the reported lines non-deterministic
-SKIP_VECTOR_CAPACITY_TESTS
-STATEMENT CALL warning_limit=2
---- ok
